data.description:
**Price Reduced** Come see this recently renovated home, completed in 2020.  Replaced Roof, HVAC, Plumbing, Electric & appliances.  Move-in ready, this ranch style home has it's primary suite on one end and THREE additional bedrooms on the other, this home adapts to your needs whether you're growing your family or expanding your investment portfolio!  Open-concept kitchen, living, and dining area - an inviting space to create cherished moments with your loved ones or envision your investment returns. From the kitchen step into the large yet comfy flex room that can be an office, den or 5th bedroom.  The kitchen boasts cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The generously sized yard beckons outdoor gatherings and leisurely days. Ideal for playtime with your kids or hosting gatherings, it's an asset for young families and investors alike.   
For those connected to NAS Jax or seeking easy access to Jacksonville's amenities, this location is unbeatable. It's not just about a home; it's about the lifestyle convenience.  
Sellers have added a Homeowners Warranty with American Home Shield Complete for one year, for added protection and peace of mind.

Don't miss this competitively priced opportunity to own a home with potential or a sound investment. In a neighborhood on the rise, this home will sell quickly!
